column5: I need to make a trip to TO.The mrs,s is working,so got all day to try some old haunts from the past. Just wondering if they are iced up.Old Mill/Erindale. PM if need be. I totally understand. Total C&R.    Thanks  B
Up to 40cm's now bud for the next 24 hours,with the traffic you'll be lucky to get there! Good luck,I took the day off already!
Credit was gin clear and full of slush today
Solid ice and broken chunk below old mill
Thanks guys.  Calling for more snow tonight.My trip may have to wait til next weekend now.
I`m afraid she`s locked up tight brother.  Drop me a line if you`re interesting in icing some big durties!
